<div id="home">
  <div class="container">
  <div class="form-group">
    {{!-- Add "Create account" and "Login" buttons --}}
    {{!-- Based on what button is pressed, display modals with fields to create account or login --}}
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="create">Create account</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="login">Login</button>

  <div class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="login-modal">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title">Login</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          {{!-- Login form --}}
             <form>
    <label for="username">Username</label>
    <p id="invalid-name"></p>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="login-username" aria-describedby="emailHelp">
    <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your info with anyone else.</small>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="password">Password</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="login-password">
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="login-button">Submit</button>
</form>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="create-modal">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title">Create account</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          {{!-- Create account form --}}
             <form>
    <label for="username">Username</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="create-username" aria-describedby="emailHelp">
    <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your info with anyone else.</small>
    <small id="username-taken" class="form-text text-muted" style="display: none">Username taken.</small>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="password">Password</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="create-password">
    <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">Do not use a secure password. Our security is bad.</small>
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="create-button">Submit</button>
</form>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-8 offset-2">
        <h1>{{msg}}</h1>
        <h2>Memory Phone!</h2>
        <h3 id="logged-in-as"></h3>
        <div class="clearfix mb-4" >
            <p>Click Here to Play!:</p>
          <button id='play-button' class="btn btn-primary float-right">Play</button>
        </div>
        <p>What is Memory Phone?</p>
        <p>Memory phone is a game like the game telephone when you were a kid. A few sentences pop up which you have to
          read quickly. Remember what they said, cause you have to type them! Once you have typed your sentences,
          someone else will have to go off of what you typed. Each game lasts 5 rounds, at the end we will show you the
          beginning and every step in between!!</p>
